Effective Date: 14/06/2024
Introduction
Welcome to the HackTheBox Walkthroughs Chrome Extension. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our extension.

Information We Collect
1- Personal Data:
Storage: We store minimal data related to the extension's functionality. This includes video solution data for HackTheBox machines and user settings.
2- Non-Personal Data:
Usage Data: We collect anonymous usage data to improve the extension's performance and user experience. This includes the frequency of use, feature usage statistics, and error reports.


How We Use Information
1- To Provide and Maintain the Service:
Store and manage video solutions and walkthrough data locally on your device.
Enhance and improve the extension's functionality and user experience.

2-To Communicate with Users:
Respond to user inquiries and support requests.


Information Sharing and Disclosure
1- Third-Party Services:
We do not share your personal data with third-party services or partners. All data remains on your local device.

2- Legal Requirements:
We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities (e.g., a court or government agency).


Data Retention
1- Local Storage:
Video solutions data and user settings are stored locally on your device and can be cleared by uninstalling the extension or manually clearing the extension's storage.

2- Usage Data:
Anonymous usage data is retained for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy.


Security
We are committed to ensuring that your information is secure. We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.


User Rights
1- Access and Control:
You have the right to access and control the data stored by the extension. You can clear the data by uninstalling the extension or manually clearing the storage.

2- Consent:
By using the HackTheBox Walkthroughs Chrome Extension, you consent to the collection and use of information as outlined in this Privacy Policy.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at slimsskhab@gmail.com.

Conclusion
Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information while providing you with a useful and efficient Chrome extension. Thank you for using HackTheBox Walkthroughs.
